    "name": "Asana Users API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The Asana Users API allows developers to interact with user data. A user object represents an account in Asana that can be given access to various workspaces, projects, and tasks. The special string identifier \"me\" can be used to refer to the current authenticated user.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Asana Support",
